{"tid":2438253,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"采頣花園實呎589呎户自由市場840萬成交","createTime":"2021-03-08T11:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T14:51:27.000Z","uid":354077,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"abcef6460a8c6c345196e8eb5d01dc45eb9b95c5","tid":2438253,"uid":354077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"新蒲崗私人參建采頤花園，罕有已補地價3房放售，業主移民減價以880萬賣樓,買家為區內家庭客，住慣不願搬離，睇樓當天議價以840萬承接。<br />\n￼&nbsp;<br />\n金滙地產分區經理密雪英表示，新近分行錄得促成新蒲崗采頤花園(自由市場)買賣成交，上述物業為6座低G室，3房 2廳間隔，座東北觀內園，建築面積691呎，實用面積589呎，日前以840萬元易手，實用呎價約14,261元。<br />\n原業主於2010年買入，當時購入價350萬，業主持貨11年，帳面獲利490萬，物業期內升值1.4倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gamway.com.hk/trannews.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamway.com.hk%2Ftrannews.php&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=f2b79f25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gamway.com.hk/trannews.php</a>"},{"pid":"9f9288331da7a87796dfbcc4c311793b7ac3fd30","tid":2438253,"uid":126663,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:25:47.000Z","msg":"根本居屋就唔應該比人補地價 <br />\n政府貼錢比人賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07d13a2271961232063ca30136a4c51b5e04529","tid":2438253,"uid":126325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"賣到咁平?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2f5ab265a675ee9f76c5243c09af7776058a48","tid":2438253,"uid":354077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f07d13a2271961232063ca30136a4c51b5e04529","tid":2438253,"uid":126325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"賣到咁平?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma